WEBVTT

00:02:28.141 --> 00:02:31.887
osećali smo se na urin i izmet,

00:02:31.911 --> 00:02:36.855
i bili smo u koncentracionom
logoru Aušvic.

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:38.634
Logoru, koji je do tada,

00:02:38.658 --> 00:02:42.434
već ubio preko milion ljudi

00:02:42.458 --> 00:02:47.101
i poslao ih kroz dimnjake na nebo.

00:02:48.379 --> 00:02:52.133
Stigli smo, oduzeli su nam
sve lične stvari,

00:02:52.157 --> 00:02:54.188
šta god smo imali,

00:02:54.212 --> 00:02:57.561
i dali nam prugaste pidžame,

00:02:57.585 --> 00:03:01.363
tetovirali nam ruke,